{"tid":2179440,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿布泰今起賣《蘋果》市民支持絡繹不絕 「係一個另類抗議」","createTime":"2020-08-29T06:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T08:14:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"daa9214a9dcdb616c60724a026d48c6c2a0c91d6","tid":2179440,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200829/4LAA6EBCOJHAVH3XLXSTQLXTWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200829%2F4LAA6EBCOJHAVH3XLXSTQLXTWQ%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=a5962c23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200829%2F4LAA6EBCOJHAVH3XLXSTQLXTWQ%2F&h=72a419b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200829/4LAA6EBCOJHAVH3XLXSTQLXTWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n中央直屬國企華潤萬家旗下的 VanGO便利店昨日起突然停售《蘋果日報》，市民質疑此舉為封殺《蘋果》，受影響報章約1000份。其後「黃店」阿布泰國生活百貨隨即宣佈在11間分店販售《蘋果》，每間預計販售100份。《蘋果》記者今早於各分店直擊開賣情況，發現特意前往阿布泰購買《蘋果》的市民絡繹不絕。"},{"pid":"ccf51ac871bb709d5eef96083c89ced9b243c062","tid":2179440,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3c7922bbb4bdfd15549292124ef14de61c5ca1","tid":2179440,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccf51ac871bb709d5eef96083c89ced9b243c062","tid":2179440,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\